{"tid":1893507,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2月24號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-02-23T10:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:51:13.000Z","uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d293b1d7e7e83ff4a18b75a4485b755ed590ad6","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:05:19.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 2 月 2 4 日 星期一】<br />\n<br />\n►--- 09:30 am ---◄ <br />\n🏛粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院 7 樓 5 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️#黃國輝裁判官<br />\n👤鄺(18)🛑<strong>已還押61天</strong> 申請保釋（#1224觀塘 管有爆炸品、管有攻擊性武器或可作非法用途的工具:nitrocellulose、煙霧彈）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n或有新案件提堂，請密切留意本頻公告"},{"pid":"73a183acc6fc5d0ad332483d806f439042058e5b","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=b7a7f588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"bc9f375c6cd5d4de40bd8945024e3c97a6af840c","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=4b4313c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=3a37d8a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"a26abf40b34d54f93566c6d8abee8e423517407a","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJuJWii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJuJWii.jpg&h=537dae00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d92148b364e58184782dcc5f65292a5943cb7ba","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"1d9c806d8616e7a40518d2c0565e1adc8dad9c9d","tid":1893507,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n粉嶺裁判法院交通<br />\n落車站: 粉嶺名都<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n青衣：279X<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n觀塘區：277X<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中西區：373，673<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺相對少對外交通，其他地區需使用黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"5dc4980bc061f1c31471c4a871f40bb6439f13f9","tid":1893507,"uid":205552,"like":